{"tid":1673200,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"生活有D迷惘, 希望大家分享下自己人生目標, 參考下","createTime":"2019-10-24T13:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T08:13:53.000Z","uid":88666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"061e4502cad81d1609a00a6299b3cd05b7d40ca5","tid":1673200,"uid":88666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:47:03.000Z","msg":"大家好呀, 我有個朋友, 佢系個平凡既港仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 24歲, 大專畢業, 月入2萬尾左右, 做下D工程管理工作, 身家？還好, 香港有個單位仔, 深圳有少少舖位同樓仔, 樣子？ 還好, 系人羣中有65分, 拍過4-5次散拖,  衣家單身中, 對於愛情婚姻生兒育女方面其實都系抱住可有可沒有的想法, 結果成日比阿爸阿媽話佢一支公條條Fing, 會後悔喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 但佢覺得衣家生活幾好呀, 假日去行山潛水睇戲試下新餐廳, 夜晚上吓進修班考下吾同牌照, 有時間就去下旅行同朋友飲下酒, 但是最近佢吾知點解覺得生活有D無聊同迷惘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 想揾吓D人生目標, 希望大家可以分享下D人生目標和方向比佢參考下, 令佢可以振作起來積極面對番人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 以及有咩方法方法可以令到佢阿爸阿媽吾好再煩住要佢拍拖既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, Thank you禁多位巴打絲打.<br />\n(9up, 勿插）"},{"pid":"babe561a325c86c67512ea94d736ec7a01fc5858","tid":1673200,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:48:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Squwor1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSquwor1.gif&h=dc4a280e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=271356c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7ab8cec1ef61b1d44752f8f7e04fa123c71f0775","tid":1673200,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:51:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9053f727085a3ef99bc4196b3afb295cc792c9a","tid":1673200,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:52:52.000Z","msg":"有沒諗過事實上